{"type": "article", "id": 20504, "title": "男性护肤品的包装设计", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-11T07:24:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152355JpUKYRI45lFENX3Q.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套男性护肤品的包装设计，来自美国包装公司 Farm Design。他们使用了土黄、橄榄绿、橙色和棕色四种接近自然的颜色为主色调，搭配以深棕色的木纹，此外还有大面积的留白，给人清新天然的感受，不会因为给男性使用而显得强势。包装的一些细微之处能见到地图，指南针等图案，有硬朗的个性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152352MyXTD04CqrJu5Iig.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152353IKCuscDUkWViY8vN.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152353ySoMfzpW4HuriKaB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.49907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152354KZfxgUXd0uGnwByJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.11574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615235429rzCTy57iUswph1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}